Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.69,0:00:04.76,OP-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(130,130)}「没有你的未来」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.06,0:00:16.86,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}守るべきものなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:26.21,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}悩むまでもなく一つしかなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.58,0:00:30.36,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}叫び声のこだま
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:39.63,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}むなしく響いた 深い森の奥に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.30,0:00:46.21,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}涙をこらえられた理由は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.16,0:00:52.75,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}重ねた指のぬくもりのせい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:56.00,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}君がいない未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.01,0:00:59.11,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}意味などない未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.83,0:01:05.17,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}二度と離したりはしないから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.89,0:01:09.74,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}君と臨む世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:12.45,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}見たことない世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.48,0:01:19.87,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}時空を越えて はるか旅する僕等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.06,0:00:16.86,OP-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}必须要守护的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:26.21,OP-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}根本不用费心思考 本来就只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.58,0:00:30.36,OP-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}呐喊的回音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:39.63,OP-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}在幽深的森林深处 空虚地回荡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.30,0:00:46.21,OP-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}能够忍住眼泪的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.16,0:00:52.75,OP-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}是与你十指相扣的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:56.00,OP-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}没有你的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.01,0:00:59.11,OP-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}毫无意义的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.83,0:01:05.17,OP-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}我不会再远你而去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.89,0:01:09.74,OP-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}与你共赴的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:12.45,OP-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}未曾见过的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.48,0:01:19.87,OP-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}穿越时空 我们继续漫长的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.30,0:01:39.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗的法术也对我无效
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:43.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,而且四魂之玉即将完成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:44.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.15,0:01:46.02,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.44,0:01:46.94,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.28,0:01:49.71,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀的碎片里面 有光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:52.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:56.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,曲灵 虽然你一直强调桔梗的法术对你无效
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.18,0:01:57.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但好像并非一点用没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.82,0:02:03.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗的光转到琥珀的碎片上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:05.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:06.24,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:08.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还来得及吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:11.98,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 还来得及 琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:15.41,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.76,0:02:18.34,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要被逼迫出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:20.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会交出碎片的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.27,0:02:21.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:26.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,转移到琥珀的碎片上的桔梗的光在给予他力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.11,0:02:30.38,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.93,0:02:31.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,把曲灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:33.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,赶出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:34.23,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:39.02,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,来得及…还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.56,0:02:40.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:49.00,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉完成之时{\fad(130,130)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:53.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:56.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:04.62,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落在那云层之中…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:06.16,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:08.18,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 切断那触手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.49,0:03:09.19,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:13.33,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:14.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.80,0:03:16.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要打倒奈落的话 就趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:18.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,给我觉悟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.68,0:03:21.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,冥道残月破
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:28.81,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,天空放晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:31.26,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:35.44,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是被污染的碎片的气息依旧在弥漫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:37.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:39.34,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:40.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,他还在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:41.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:52.29,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜 你们输了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.61,0:03:54.66,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:56.34,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.66,0:03:57.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:00.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的身体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:02.36,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,爆碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:10.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:11.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:14.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.39,0:04:15.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:21.08,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,被爆碎牙斩过的身体无法再用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:24.54,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了啊 曲灵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:31.19,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎你让梦幻之白夜当幌子 用尽办法想避开我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:34.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我这把天生牙就那么可怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:38.62,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,能够斩杀曲灵的只有杀生丸的天生牙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:41.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,然后只要曲灵被消灭了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.89,0:04:43.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我被封印了的灵力就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:46.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 别让我笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:50.88,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那个天生牙 不是没能一击将我杀死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:52.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不是没能把你杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:54.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是没有把你杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:03.97,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让你清楚地明白自己是被谁杀死的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:07.08,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,天生牙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.59,0:05:13.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:16.89,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,别以为这样就完结了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:18.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:20.36,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我还…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:23.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没有完结？什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:26.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是虚张声势
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:30.17,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是说曲灵还没有完全死去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:31.61,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:39.94,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,铃 铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:43.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:45.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:47.43,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,请听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:50.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,法师大人吸了曲灵的毒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.69,0:05:54.36,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,而且铃也中了曲灵的毒 还在昏迷中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:00.44,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 我们也会去村里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:02.13,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我担心法师大人他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:02.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:04.47,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,走了 戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:05.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:08.01,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:12.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:18.26,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 你的灵力似乎还没恢复啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:21.32,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我虽然一直待在结界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.37,0:06:24.16,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但你完全不知道我的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:26.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:29.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,呵 怎么了 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.46,0:06:31.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,痛快地砍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:34.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧 我不会杀她的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.57,0:06:38.01,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在拿到琥珀的碎片之前是不会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:40.61,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,会让你得逞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:45.09,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚啊 我现在被你在粉碎着的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:47.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是随时都可以舍弃的部份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:51.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才犬夜叉使出的冥道残月破
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:54.09,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,还有杀生丸的爆碎牙斩到的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:55.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,同样是不需要的部份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:03.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落以为我没有灵力 对我没有防备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:07.47,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我还留着寻找四魂之玉的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:10.97,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落体内的四魂之玉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:13.36,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,只要直接攻击那个应该就能给他致命一击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:14.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:15.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,头？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:16.58,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,颈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:18.49,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,还是心脏？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.47,0:07:22.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:24.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉在奈落的右肩上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:31.98,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,还留着这种程度的灵力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:33.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:35.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:37.71,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,又是那个结界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:40.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你要怎么做 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:43.32,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,比起戈薇的性命 你更想保住碎片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:46.79,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不交出琥珀的碎片的话 戈薇就会死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:49.73,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,耍什么小聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:50.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:52.34,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:56.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉的铁碎牙只能使出会牵涉到戈薇的大招
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:58.62,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不过飞来骨的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:02.09,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,碎片在…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:04.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚 右肩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:04.94,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:10.74,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,红色铁碎牙？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:13.59,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样 只要配合默契
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:15.38,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:17.58,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:21.18,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:28.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:30.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:33.76,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:35.09,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:38.02,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,能够粉碎邪气的飞来骨竟然没有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.42,0:08:43.01,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:45.69,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,魍魉丸的铠甲？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:47.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,注意到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:53.46,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有在众多妖怪中最坚硬的铠甲-冥王兽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.27,0:08:57.24,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,魍魉丸吞噬了这只妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:09:00.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,折断杀生丸的闘鬼神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.49,0:09:04.31,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你的铁碎牙也无可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:08.98,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我奈落把魍魉丸吞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:13.14,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉被这铠甲保护着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:17.48,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我是特地受下你们的攻击的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:21.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让你们明白这只不过是徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:25.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀 除了把你的碎片交上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:27.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没有别的方法能够拯救戈薇的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:30.43,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇小姐的性命…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:35.38,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 被他的话迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:42.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这么快就醒了吗 真不愧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:47.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然被封印了 但奈落依旧惧怕戈薇的灵力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.29,0:09:50.22,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要从中找到取胜的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:52.62,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救戈薇的性命的方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.79,0:09:55.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:59.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇小姐被奈落袭击时丢落的箭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:01.09,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好像在发光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:07.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 现在在我的碎片之中有桔梗大人的一丝光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:10.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,贪生怕死了吗 琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.43,0:10:13.74,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,牺牲戈薇也要保住性命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:16.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑 琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:18.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我会救戈薇的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:22.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:25.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 要被吸进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:27.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,犬…犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:29.66,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,等着 我现在就去救你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:32.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像还不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:34.58,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,知道谁才领导一切吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.39,0:10:36.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,承诺我 奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:40.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:41.59,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:45.62,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要我给你碎片 你就要承诺放过戈薇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:48.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:49.97,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:51.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.89,0:10:53.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不能来 琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.89,0:10:56.19,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落是不会放过我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:59.77,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 如果留住你性命的四魂之玉被取走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:01.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:04.81,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,反正是原本就不存在的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:06.36,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不会吝惜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:09.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不存在的性命…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:13.14,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫你跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.34,0:11:15.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不要被奈落的话欺骗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:17.87,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 这里就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:19.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.90,0:11:25.48,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,乖 琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.96,0:11:29.66,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在亲手杀死父亲与同伴的那天…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:32.24,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你就已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:34.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是心灵还是身体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:41.97,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我一直在想 如果那天就这样死去该多轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:43.34,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:48.04,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我每天都只想着死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.83,0:11:51.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 现在不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:54.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐和犬夜叉少爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:56.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,都叫我活着去面对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:59.38,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会救出戈薇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.27,0:12:02.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗大人的光芒和戈薇小姐的箭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.01,0:12:04.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,由我的手连系着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:07.18,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:10.73,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落 我要打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:12.34,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:23.29,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:28.43,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙和飞来骨都不能弄碎的铠甲…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:29.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,正在崩坏…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:31.24,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:33.94,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,从箭中流出光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:37.99,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这是琥珀的碎片之中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.53,0:12:39.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗的光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:44.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,如果继续跟琥珀接触的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:46.02,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就会被净化之光吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:48.87,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:51.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:55.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就爆掉奈落的头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:57.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,金刚枪破
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:02.22,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:08.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:09.17,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:17.29,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落逃进云层之中了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:18.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:27.57,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:29.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.84,0:13:35.86,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:37.59,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你真努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:41.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 其实我还在犹豫着…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.64,0:13:44.09,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 我可以活下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.71,0:13:48.19,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你必须活下去 琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.49,0:13:51.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,活着来赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.75,0:13:59.19,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒 你起来真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:02.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 让你担心了啊 七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.51,0:14:03.54,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,法师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:08.23,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,方才法师大人的身体中渗出不详的气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:12.77,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那有可能是法师大人吸进去的曲灵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.02,0:14:14.39,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:17.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,现在难以相信地觉得舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:20.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是犬夜叉他们把曲灵干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:22.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:28.43,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 让我担心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:30.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 邪见大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.11,0:14:32.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:35.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是你一个人的问题啊 铃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:38.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在杀生丸大人外出的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:40.81,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你出什么事了 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:41.33,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:44.08,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你在听吗 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:56.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,什… 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:14:58.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么…你要去哪 铃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:00.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:05.16,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:07.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:15.23,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:16.31,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.82,0:15:19.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不过琥珀的一击应该相当见效
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:21.39,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.59,0:15:22.81,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,多得你我才得救
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:24.04,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:26.04,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.31,0:15:28.56,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你能跟我们一起了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.81,0:15:29.91,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.44,0:15:35.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我的罪孽并没有消亡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:37.87,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我已经不会再逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:39.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我要正视我的罪孽坚强生活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:44.46,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,今后一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:55.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 琥珀的碎片…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:02.41,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.99,0:16:03.76,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:04.98,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:07.13,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:10.98,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,保住性命的四魂之玉…没了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.91,0:16:12.74,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.77,0:16:14.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:19.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:21.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.11,0:16:25.19,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.95,0:16:27.66,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还来得及吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:30.23,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.99,0:17:07.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,邪恶的黑暗再次合而为一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:16.94,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗的光也被清除了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.38,0:17:20.43,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀的碎片充满污秽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:25.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,完全的四魂之玉 我终于得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:27.69,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,铃她…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:29.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,被拐走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.41,0:17:31.09,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 法师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:33.61,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,从你身体里面渗出来的邪气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:35.66,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,铃被那邪气包着…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:38.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 是曲灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:42.17,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是曲灵把铃带走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.40,0:17:45.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,邪见 有你跟着怎么还发生这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.95,0:17:46.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:49.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 要逃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:54.13,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,如果杀生丸大人回来了 我毫无疑问会被杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:55.46,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就趁现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:17:57.44,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,曲灵还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:01.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:02.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:03.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,果然？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:10.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸 「还活着」是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:14.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,曲灵的本体潜伏在法师的身体里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:20.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,回答一句也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:23.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,一如既往 是个冷淡的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:26.59,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不看我一眼就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:29.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,铃现在是这么危险吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.56,0:18:37.56,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,曲灵会把铃带到奈落那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.96,0:18:39.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,目的只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:44.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,封住我杀生丸的天生牙和爆碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:58.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 奈落在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:00.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落在哪里！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.68,0:19:13.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:16.39,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我看见奈落漆黑的四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:18.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我的破魔之箭…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:21.89,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就算灵力还没有恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.92,0:19:24.96,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,还是可以引导犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:28.81,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:32.01,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,冥道残月破
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:37.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.44,0:19:42.39,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 了解到自己的无能了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:46.04,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀你也没能拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:48.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,跟那时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:51.14,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,跟没能拯救桔梗的那时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:54.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗的光也清除了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:58.91,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀的碎片被我的污秽充斥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:08.61,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:12.24,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在四魂之玉之中桔梗的一丝光芒消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:26.18,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:27.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:33.38,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:36.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:55.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:08.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.17,0:21:11.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.31,0:21:13.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.51,0:21:19.01,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗的光离开碎片 留在了琥珀的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.74,0:21:20.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.77,0:21:24.86,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,比起消灭奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:27.94,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗还是选择了拯救琥珀的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:34.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:36.76,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.98,0:21:49.16,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,与奈落的战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:53.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,交托在我们的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:02.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:02.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,
